ared to the latter, we find a slightly\nreduced uncertainty and a larger central value, with its central value lying at\nthe lower edge of our uncertainty band.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2015 18:16:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Nov 2015 09:05:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 27 Nov 2015 11:51:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-27"}
