ys. Finally, we discuss our results in the context of\nobserved Galactic supernova remnants such as 3C391 and the Cygnus Loop.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Aug 2015 20:14:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-17"}
