 theory. More\nprecisely, we prove a hydrodynamic limit result for some gradient processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Aug 2015 03:56:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 19 Mar 2016 00:17:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-22"}
